Amy Watson joined Code.org in early 2020 as Director of Finance to lead strategic and operational Finance for the organization, overseeing financial reporting, forecasting and accounting functions.

Prior to Code.org, Amy played a major role in a multitude of successful M&A, financing, and strategic planning activities in the technology and software industries. Her years of expertise in FP&A bring a forward-looking, analytical approach to Code.org, where her skills can be used to support her belief in the power of education to uplift.

Amy holds a BA in Business Administration from Seattle University and an MBA from Loyola University Chicago.
